OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. The rest of the night
OL,7,Fwill be mainly dry although rather
OL,8,Fcloudy, perhaps the odd shower
OL,9,Fbreaking out in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FStarting off dry but rain
OL,12,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,13,Ffor a time, clearing the southeast
OL,14,Flate afternoon. A mild start but
OL,15,Fturning colder during the afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,18,Ffor most of Thursday but patchy rain
OL,19,Fpossible in the evening. Unsettled
OL,20,Fwith showers or longer spells of rain
OL,21,Fon Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
